'''Simon Vuwa Kaunda''' is a member of the [[Pan-African Parliament]] from [[Malawi]] and a member of the [[National Assembly of Malawi]] as part of the ruling [[Democratic Progressive Party (Malawi)|Democratic Progressive Party]].

